      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·006.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">行露.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>厭浥行露，豈不夙夜，謂行多露。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Wet lay the dew on the path:
Might I not have walked there in the early dawn?
But I said there was too much dew on the path.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-zhaonan-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879-fulltext">
      <prop type="x-work-id">shijing</prop>
