      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·召南·006.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">行露.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>誰謂鼠無牙？何以穿我墉？誰謂女無家？何以速我訟？雖速我訟，亦不女從。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Who can say that the rat has no molar teeth?
How else could it bore through my wall?
Who can say that you did not get me betrothed?
How else could you have urged on this trial?
But though you have forced me to trial,
I will still not follow you.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
